document.full_text: southwest airlines is willing to expand inspections for its older boeing 737 aircraft but sees no reason for concern a week after one of its jets made an emergency landing with a hole in its fuselage, the discount carrier's chief executive officer said on friday.
document.title: southwest airlines sees narrow concern over 737 jet
